Package processors

Class Processor

  • java.lang.Object
    • processors.Processor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProcessor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReverseProcessor, ShellProcessor
    public abstract class Processor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IProcessor
    An abstract class implementing some behaviour for the IProcessor interface. Implementations are provided for all methods of IProcessor except for merge.
